imdb.plot outline: Rodney Yee's Yoga for Energy & Stress Relief, filmed in picturesque Western Colorado, features restorative yoga practices designed to calm the mind and gently energize the body. Perfect for anyone who wants to reduce stress and increase focus.

Rodney Yee's Yoga for Energy & Stress Relief, filmed in picturesque Western Colorado, features three 20-minute restorative yoga practices designed to calm the mind and gently energize the body. Perfect for anyone who wants to reduce stress and increase focus.
